	(3, 'Bali Half Day Tours', '<p>Bali Half Day Tours is wonderful tour packages to visit interesting places in Bali Island with private air conditioning car and professional English speaking driver to give you the right information during the tour. The trip will be visit the unique attractions, cultures and daily life of Balinese people, Our friendly driver has been experience for handling short day trips and more familiar with what happening in Bali, all route tourism sites and for sure is the expert in giving the best service. Duration of the Bali Half Day Tours normally is six until seven hours and defend of the packages you choose.</p>', 'half.jpg'),
	(4, 'BALI FULL DAY TOURS', '<p>Bali Full Day Tours is a great one day tour that we design for traveler who want to explore Bali Island, we design the trip to visit East Bali, North Bali, Central Bali, West Bali or Southern Part of Bali in one day. The packages that we design is to make easier for traveler to planning their holidays with flexible time arrangement during visiting places of interest on the program of our packages. The trips will visiting unique cultures and amazing view of beautiful panorama such as Balinese Dance, Rice Terrace, Volcano, Lake, Mountain, Hot Spring, Waterfall, Beach and spectacular sunset or sunrise.</p>\r\n<p>Bali is very popular in the world as number one tourist destination in Asia, that\'s why on our Bali Full Day Tours we make the best packages that you can see in one day for your memorable experience. Enjoy our Bali Full Day Tours package with our professional Bali Tour Driver which is very friendly inform you about the beautiful panorama of tourist sites and other tourist destinations by performing their outstanding service together for your convenience and enjoyable during the tour. Start from IDR 550,000 Per Person All Inclusive and the trip that we design is very flexible, if you would like to pass the itinerary you may inform to our driver and you may replace with other tourist destination.</p>', ''),
	(5, 'BALI TOUR PACKAGES', '<p>Bali Tour Packages are the comprehensive range of tours, sightseeing and travel guides to visit places of interest in Bali and visit the unique attractions, cultures, traditional Balinese social life and all about tourist activities. Our professional tour driver are friendly guiding you to visit the beautiful panorama of tourist sites and other tourist destinations by performing his outstanding service and enjoyable tour journey.</p>\r\n<p>Bali Tour Packages are compiled in such programs offer you to give the wide opportunity and impressive experience. Trip around Bali Island is an experience to see the Bali &ndash; Indonesia with unique cultures and places of interest. In this site, we have provided the packages which are assigned with the high value and unforgettable experience to be enjoyed during your vacation in Bali. Start from IDR 2,500,000 per person, the itinerary is flexible if you would like to pass the itinerary or add with other places you may inform to our guide and he will give their best service and information during your tour with us.</p>', ''),
	(6, 'BALI ROUND TRIP', '<p>Bali Round Trip is design for traveler to discover the unique Balinese culture and explore the complete beauty of Bali island. The charming people and the gracious smiling of the people will make your holiday never enough in Bali. A lot of interesting places to visit which is available on in every corner in Bali, you will always find something interesting to see in every places such as the people way of life, cultural activities and of course the nature needs your some times to spend for. It is sometimes said you need at least 2 weeks holiday to know glance information about all interesting places available in this island.</p>\r\n<p>Bali Round Trip program is the best way to explore Bali in deeper way, you will get at least the main highlight of the island. You might see the extraordinary places un-common for tourist so far and sure you will meet the innocent faces of villager and their warmest welcome to every visitors. Experiencing the complete beauty of Bali is no longer involving unnecessary hustles and bustles with our best round tip packages. Start from IDR 5,200,000 per person, the packages that we made is complete with hotel accommodation, breakfast, lunch, all entrance ticket and English speaking driver.</p>', ''),
	(7, 'BALI HONEYMOON PACKAGES', '<p>Bali Honeymoon Packages offer the best holiday packages in paradise island with many opportunities to get the best privacy, leisure and pleasure that Bali has to offer. The happy couples will be able to spend precious quality time together, the packages features excellent accommodations combines with exquisite natural beauties of Bali, rich culture with exciting indoor and outdoor activities to turn your romantic honeymoon into a wonderful experience. Whether you plan to celebrate one of the most special days in your life with a honeymoon in Bali or you just want a romantic place to escape with that special someone.</p>\r\n<p>These stunning Bali Honeymoon Packages are renowned for their intimate atmosphere. Start from IDR 7,500,000 per person, the services given from beginning to end of your holiday, we make sure your honeymoon vacation which you&rsquo;ve always dreaming to take every measure to ensure bliss. What you\'ll find here at our packages are the very best choices around because we carefully to select the hotels that provide the top service and value - superior accommodation at great prices. Just look through our great range of Honeymoon Packages, find the ideal one for you then book on our bookings page.</p>', '');

