	(14, 6, 'BALI ROUND TRIP 7 DAYS AND 6 NIGHTS', '<p style="text-align: justify;">Bali Round Trip 7 Days and 6 Nights is one of the most popular Bali Round Trip that we design for traveler on their holidays with amazing experience to visit places of interest in Bali Island which is popular with it\'s art and culture. It is not an exaggeration that when a Balinese is asked what heaven is like, he would say just like Bali, without the worries of mundane life. We fully ensure your time with us will be extraordinary and more amusing than you&rsquo;ve ever imagined. The trip packages that we offer is a reasonable price where inside of the package is complete with hotel accommodation, private air conditioning car, entrance ticket, lunch and safety driver who will guiding you during the trips. The tour will be very comfortable with our private air conditioning car transfer and to keep your convenience and enjoyable journey our professional tour driver and guide is always outstanding offer his best service with the information you need.</p>', '<p><strong>Price :&nbsp;IDR 6,000,000&nbsp;per person</strong></p>', '<p>Day 01 : Arrival in Bali<br>Day 02 : Barong Dance - Goa Lawah Temple - East Bali Tour<br>Day 03 : Besakih Temple - Kintamani Volcano - Banjar Hot Spring Tour<br>Day 04 : Dolphin Watching - Jatiluwih Rice Terrace - Tanah Lot Sunset Tour<br>Day 05 : Ubud Monkey Forest - Ubud Art Market - Bajra Sandhi Monument Tour<br>Day 06 : Padang Padang Beach - Uluwatu Temple - Kecak and Fire Dance Tour<br>Day 07 : Departure</p>', '<p><strong>Price Include :</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<div align="justify">6 Nights stay at the hotel below</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div align="justify">Private Transport with Fully Air-Conditioning Car</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div align="justify">Itinerary as on Bali Round Trip</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div align="justify">Professional English Speaking Driver</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div align="justify">Entrance Fee in Tourism Object</div>